CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 16, 1954, pg. 9, reads: "Dinner For Mrs. Mueller - Pittsburgh Delta Sigma Theta sorors got together last Wednesday night at Loendi Club and gave an intimate little dinner for Soror Ruth Caston Mueller and invited as guest, her hostess, Mrs. Alma Illery. Pictured, clock-wise, Sorors Florence May, Mary Baltimore, president of Alpha Epsilon Chapter; Toki S. Johnson, Ruth Caston Mueller, Mrs. Illery, Sorors Daisy E. Lampkin, Shady Crossland, Nancy Lee and Mabel Lewis.  The Deltas gift to Mrs. Mueller was a leather traveling clock. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Florence May, Mary Baltimore, Toki Schalk Johnson, Ruth Caston Mueller, Alma Illery, Daisy E. Lampkin, Shady Crossland, Nancy Lee, and Mabel Lewis gathered around dining table in Loendi Club
